00:12:48.141 --> 00:12:54.100
<i>Srta. Jerusha Bromley
Walpole, New Hampshire, USA</i>


210
00:12:59.580 --> 00:13:01.140
<i>É ele, não é?</i>

211
00:13:01.220 --> 00:13:02.700
